OL,3,CBorders museum named in top 10% of
OL,4,Cglobal visitor attractions
OL,6,FA Borders museum has scored a hat-
OL,7,Ftrick of success after being named as
OL,8,Fone of the top 10 percent of visitor
OL,9,Fattractions globally.
OL,11,FThe Great Tapestry of Scotland has
OL,12,Fbeen named as a winner of the
OL,13,FTripadvisor Travellers' Choice Awards
OL,14,Ffor the third year running.
OL,16,FThe Galashiels visitor centre is
OL,17,Fmanaged by charitable trust Live
OL,18,FBorders, which oversees culture,
OL,19,Fheritage, and leisure facilities
OL,20,Facross the region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
