PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778193332
OL,3,CBorders museum named in top 10% of
OL,4,Cglobal visitor attractions
OL,6,FThe award winners are chosen based on
OL,7,Freviews and ratings from travellers
OL,8,Fover the past 12 months.
OL,10,FSandy Maxwell-Forbes, visitor
OL,11,Fattraction manager at Live Borders,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Every review helps others
OL,13,Fdiscover the magic and beauty of The
OL,14,FGreat Tapestry of Scotland and the
OL,15,Fstories it holds, and we are truly
OL,16,Fgrateful for this continued
OL,17,Fencouragement."
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@OO]
