OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778193332
OL,3,CBorders museum named in top 10% of
OL,4,Cglobal visitor attractions
OL,6,FThe Great Tapestry of Scotland,
OL,7,Fstitched by a thousand volunteers
OL,8,Facross the country, depicts the
OL,9,Fhistory of Scotland from millions of
OL,10,Fyears BC to the present day.
OL,12,FThe idea was first conceived by author
OL,13,FAlexander McCall Smith, who worked in
OL,14,Fcollaboration with artist Andrew
OL,15,FCrummy and historian Alastair Moffat
OL,16,Fto create the visual and narrative
OL,17,Fstructure of the tapestry.
OL,19,FIt remains one of the biggest
OL,20,Fcommunity arts projects undertaken in
OL,21,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
