PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778193332
OL,3,CBorders museum named in top 10% of
OL,4,Cglobal visitor attractions
OL,6,FThe visitor centre includes a gallery
OL,7,Fspecifically built to house the
OL,8,Ftapestry, a temporary gallery, a shop,
OL,9,Fand a cafe.
OL,11,FThe architectural design of the
OL,12,Fcentre, which opened in 2021, was
OL,13,Finspired by the roofscape of towers,
OL,14,Fdormers, gables, and pitched roofs
OL,15,Fseen in Galashiels.
OL,17,FMr Maxwell-Forbes added: "It is a
OL,18,Fgreat honour to preserve the memories
OL,19,Fof a nation for the world to discover.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
